{"_id":"HdlssHorse001yze","name":"The Headless Horseman","type":"npc","img":"icons/magic/death/ghost-horse-white.webp","system":{"health":{"value":12,"max":12,"autoCalc":false},"resolve":{"value":0,"max":0,"autoCalc":false},"specialAttackTableUuid":"","description":"An infamous spectral figure haunting the darkest corners of Sleepy Hollow. Mounted on a jet-black stallion, clad in a dark tattered cloak, he carries a jack-o'-lantern as his ghastly visage. Relentless in pursuit, seeking vengeance.\n\nArmor Rating: 2 (tattered cloak and supernatural resilience)\nSpeed: 3 (on foot), 5 (mounted)\n\nSpecial Traits: Spectral Mount (immune to fear/fatigue, Health 10, AR 2), Decapitating Strike (+3 dmg on successful melee, instant decapitation at 0 HP), Phantom Charge (move through obstacles), Fear Aura (Fear check each round, Short range), Regeneration (2 HP/round unless holy/blessed weapons)\n\nWeaknesses: Sacred Ground (3 dmg/round, no regeneration), Holy Weapons (double damage)"},"prototypeToken":{"name":"The Headless Horseman","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayName":20},"items":[{"_id":"HhStr001yzegen","name":"Strength","type":"attribute","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","system":{"slug":"strength","value":6,"current":6,"category":"Physical","description":"","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhAgi001yzegen","name":"Agility","type":"attribute","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","system":{"slug":"agility","value":5,"current":5,"category":"Physical","description":"","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhWit001yzegen","name":"Wits","type":"attribute","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","system":{"slug":"wits","value":3,"current":3,"category":"Mental","description":"","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhEmp001yzegen","name":"Empathy","type":"attribute","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","system":{"slug":"empathy","value":0,"current":0,"category":"Social","description":"","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhMel001yzegen","name":"Melee","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","system":{"slug":"melee","value":6,"linkedAttribute":"strength","description":"","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhRid001yzegen","name":"Riding","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","system":{"slug":"riding","value":5,"linkedAttribute":"agility","description":"","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhInt001yzegen","name":"Intimidation","type":"skill","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","system":{"slug":"intimidation","value":4,"linkedAttribute":"empathy","description":"","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhBla001yzegen","name":"Spectral Blade","type":"weapon","img":"icons/weapons/swords/sword-broad-silver.webp","system":{"bonusDice":3,"grip":"2H","damage":3,"range":"engaged","weight":1,"price":0,"isRanged":false,"currentReloads":0,"maxReloads":0,"linkedAttribute":"strength","linkedSkill":"melee","tagIds":[],"description":""},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhAr001yzegen","name":"Tattered Cloak & Supernatural Resilience","type":"armor","img":"icons/equipment/chest/breastplate-layered-steel.webp","system":{"armorRating":2,"weight":0,"price":0,"description":"AR 2 — Tattered cloak and supernatural resilience","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhSpe001yzegen","name":"Spectral Mount","type":"special-trait","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"description":"The horse is a spectral creature, immune to fear and fatigue. Health 10, Armor Rating 2.","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhDec001yzegen","name":"Decapitating Strike","type":"special-trait","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"description":"On a successful melee attack, can inflict +3 damage. If this reduces a target to 0 Health, they are instantly decapitated.","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhPha001yzegen","name":"Phantom Charge","type":"special-trait","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"description":"Can move through obstacles and difficult terrain without hindrance. Can make a melee attack at end of movement.","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhFea001yzegen","name":"Fear Aura","type":"special-trait","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"description":"All creatures within Short range must make a Fear check each round. Those who fail suffer a -2 penalty to all actions until out of range.","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhReg001yzegen","name":"Regeneration","type":"special-trait","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"description":"Regenerates 2 Health per round unless damaged by holy or blessed weapons.","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhSac001yzegen","name":"Sacred Ground (Weakness)","type":"weakness","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"Cannot enter consecrated or hallowed ground. Takes 3 damage per round if forced in. Regeneration does not work there.","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}},{"_id":"HhHol001yzegen","name":"Holy Weapons (Weakness)","type":"weakness","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"Weapons blessed by a priest or imbued with holy power deal double damage.","tagIds":[]},"flags":{}}],"flags":{}}
